<headline>Special Weather Statement issued December 15 at 9:31PM MST  by NWS GreatFalls</headline>
<description>...Light snow through Midnight...
An area of light snow will affect the Interstate 15 corridor from
Craig to just south of Helena through Midnight.
Visibility will fall down to one mile at times, with new snow
accumulations up to one inch.
Those traveling along Interstate 15 from Helena to Craig should be
alert for areas of poor visibility and snow covered roadways.</description>
